author: Brock Cardiner
title: The New ‘Wonder Woman’ Trailer Tells the Origin Story of Diana
text:
The latest Wonder Woman trailer has arrived and the 2.5-minute clip takes us into Diana’s past to show us how she became the hero we all know. Now just three months away from the film’s premiere, the trailer shows us a younger version of the Batman v Superman heroine, played by Gal Gadot, and takes us on her personal journey, from princess of the Amazons to London legend.
Enjoy the trailer above and look for the film to open on June 2. Watch the previous two trailers below.
